The paper involves a new AI task that requires a range of skills including active perception, language understanding, goal-driven navigation, commonsense reasoning, and grounding of language into actions. These skills are relevant to several sub-categories of computer science, including artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), and machine learning (cs.LG). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
